1.0.name: wordpress/lingonberry
1.0.description: A clean and simple theme for bloggers. Features responsive design, custom styling for all post formats, custom page templates (Archive, Contact), custom widgets (video, Flickr and Dribbble) and translation-ready code. Available translations: Swedish/svenska.
